  </entry>
  
  <entry>
    <title>使用 Android Studio 建立 Flutter 專案</title>
    <link href="https://yabai.tw/flutter/general/counter/studio/"/>
    <id>https://yabai.tw/flutter/general/counter/studio/</id>
    <published>2024-08-07T01:29:20.000Z</published>
    <updated>2024-08-07T07:08:29.085Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Flutter 可以使用多種方式建立專案，本文介紹使用 Android Studio 建立 Flutter 專案。</p><a id="more"></a><h2 id="Version"><a href="#Version" class="headerlink" title="Version"></a>Version</h2><p>Android Studio 2024.1.1</p><h2 id="New-Flutter-Project"><a href="#New-Flutter-Project" class="headerlink" title="New Flutter Project"></a>New Flutter Project</h2><p><img src="/images/flutter/general/counter/studio/studio01.webp" alt="overview001"></p><ul><li>Android Studio 安裝 Flutter plugin 之後，會多了 <code>New Flutter Project</code>，以此建立 Flutter 專案</li></ul><p><img src="/images/flutter/general/counter/studio/studio02.webp" alt="overview002"></p><ul><li>選 <code>Flutter</code> 設定 Flutter SDK 路徑</li></ul><blockquote><p>當使用 Homebrew 管理 Flutter SDK 時，可方便切換 Flutter 版本，但路徑較為特別，Homebrew 會將 Flutter SDK 放在 <code>/opt/homebrew/Caskroom</code> 下</p></blockquote><p><img src="/images/flutter/general/counter/studio/studio03.webp" alt="overview003"></p><ul><li><code>Project name</code>：只能使用 <code>snake case</code> 命名法，不能使用 <code>camel case</code> 或 <code>kebab case</code>，因為 project name 會拿來當 module name，且 Dart 的 module 只能以 <code>snake case</code> 命名</li><li><code>Plateforms</code>：勾選 <code>Android</code>、<code>iOS</code>、<code>macOS</code>、<code>Web</code></li></ul><h2 id="Web"><a href="#Web" class="headerlink" title="Web"></a>Web</h2><p><img src="/images/flutter/general/counter/studio/studio04.webp" alt="overview004"></p><ul><li><code>Device</code>：<code>Chrome (Web)</code></li><li><code>Run</code>：開始編譯執行</li></ul><p><img src="/images/flutter/general/counter/studio/studio05.webp" alt="overview005"></p><ul><li>在 Chrome 執行經典 counter</li></ul><h2 id="macOS"><a href="#macOS" class="headerlink" title="macOS"></a>macOS</h2><p><img src="/images/flutter/general/counter/studio/studio06.webp" alt="overview006"></p><ul><li><code>Device</code>：<code>macOS (desktop)</code></li><li><code>Run</code>：開始編譯執行</li></ul><p><img src="/images/flutter/general/counter/studio/studio07.webp" alt="overview007"></p><ul><li>在 macOS 執行經典 counter</li></ul><h2 id="iOS"><a href="#iOS" class="headerlink" title="iOS"></a>iOS</h2><p><img src="/images/flutter/general/counter/studio/studio08.webp" alt="overview008"></p><ul><li><code>Device</code>：選擇 <code>Open iOS Simulator</code> 先執行 iOS Simulator</li></ul><p><img src="/images/flutter/general/counter/studio/studio09.webp" alt="overview009"></p><ul><li>將 iOS Simulator 跑起來</li></ul><p><img src="/images/flutter/general/counter/studio/studio10.webp" alt="overview010"></p><ul><li><code>Device</code>：選擇 iPhone 15 Pro Max (mobile)</li><li><code>Run</code>：開始編譯執行</li></ul><p><img src="/images/flutter/general/counter/studio/studio11.webp" alt="overview011"></p><ul><li>在 iOS 執行經典 counter</li></ul><h2 id="Android"><a href="#Android" class="headerlink" title="Android"></a>Android</h2><p><img src="/images/flutter/general/counter/studio/studio12.webp" alt="overview012"></p><ul><li>在 Device Manage 啟動 AVD</li></ul><p><img src="/images/flutter/general/counter/studio/studio13.webp" alt="overview013"></p><ul><li>在 Running Devices 按下 power 啟動 Android</li></ul><p><img src="/images/flutter/general/counter/studio/studio14.webp" alt="overview014"></p><ul><li><code>Device</code>：選擇 Android 14 (mobile)</li><li><code>Run</code>：開始編譯執行</li></ul><p><img src="/images/flutter/general/counter/studio/studio15.webp" alt="overview015"></p><ul><li>在 Android 執行經典 counter</li></ul><h2 id="Conclusion"><a href="#Conclusion" class="headerlink" title="Conclusion"></a>Conclusion</h2><ul><li>相同的 codebase 可同時在 Web、macOS、iOS 與 Android 執行</li></ul>]]></content>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;Flutter 可以使用多種方式建立專案，本文介紹使用 Android Studio 建立 Flutter 專案。&lt;/p&gt;</summary>
    
    
    
    
